## What is LIT?

The Leaders in Training program is designed for High School Students (Finished 9th grade - Graduating Seniors) to experience an incredible adventure of following Christ and developing their leadership skills.

Through first-hand experience and hands-on learning, you will be able to focus on your God-given skills while strengthening your faith, growing in community, and becoming servant-hearted leaders who are mission-minded.

{% ctaButton
